這是波伊爾在英國達人參赛成名前，於1999年為西洛錫安學校慶祝2000年[[千禧年|千禧年]]來臨而制作的慈善唱片獻唱了一首{{link-en|失戀歌|Torch song}}《Cry Me a River》，這唱片限量1000張，當時的西洛錫安郵報就評價波伊爾的演繹令他拿到唱片後不停讓這首歌在唱機中不停重播，波伊爾在英國達人演唱《I Dreamed a Dream》後她的《Cry Me a River》亦隨即被上傳到網上，2009年紐約郵報報道這個故事的標題寫道「蘇珊·波伊爾不是黔驢技窮（Susan Boyle: No One-Trick Pony）」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foreveramber.co.uk/2009/04/susan-boyle-of-britains-got-talent-i-knew-her-when.html|title=Susan Boyle of Britain’s Got Talent: I knew her when…(Cry Me a River)|author=Amber McNaught|date=2000年|accessdate=2009-11-28|archive-date=2009-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091211230951/http://www.foreveramber.co.uk/2009/04/susan-boyle-of-britains-got-talent-i-knew-her-when.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/blogs/popwrap/item_MpB0k4g4XipELw2MX5fmXP|title=Susan Boyle: No One-Trick Pony|publisher=紐約郵報|date=2009-07-13|accessdate=2009-11-28|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026124346/http://www.nypost.com/p/blogs/popwrap/item_MpB0k4g4XipELw2MX5fmXP|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

;專輯《[[我曾有夢|I Dreamed a Dream]]》、[[單曲|單曲]]《I Dreamed a Dream》和《{{link-en|野馬 (歌曲)|Wild Horses (song)|Wild Horses}}》
2009年11月23日Syco發售的波伊爾出道[[音樂專輯|專輯]]《I Dreamed a Dream》於同年9月4日預售，12首歌曲中主要收錄[[翻唱|翻唱]]作、3首基督教圣詩和1首原創作品。它成為了[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]]最佳預售唱片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/news/2009/09/04/susan-boyle-s-debut-album-at-number-one-three-months-before-it-s-released-115875-21646196/|title=Susan Boyle's debut album at number one - three months before it's released|publisher=Mirror.co.uk|date=2009-09-04|accessdate=2009-11-28|archive-date=2009-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091128214937/http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/news/2009/09/04/susan-boyle-s-debut-album-at-number-one-three-months-before-it-s-released-115875-21646196/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並登上[[英國專輯排行榜|英國]]<ref name="ukchart">{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8385395.stm|publisher=bbc.co.uk|title=Susan Boyle's debut album makes UK chart history|accessdate=2009-11-30|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042417/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8385395.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|愛爾蘭專輯排行榜|Irish Albums Chart|愛爾蘭}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/album/52113|publisher=aCharts.us|title=Susan Boyle - I Dreamed A Dream|accessdate=2009-11-27|archive-date=2010-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205050120/http://acharts.us/album/52113|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[Billboard_200|美國]]、[[澳洲音樂銷量排行榜|澳洲]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/performer/susan_boyle|title=Susan Boyle|publisher=|access-date=2009-12-06|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330095253/http://acharts.us/performer/susan_boyle|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[紐西蘭唱片業協會|新西蘭]]<ref name="nz">{{cite web|url=http://www.rianz.org.nz/rianz/chart.asp|title=New Zealand Chart: Chart #1697|date=2009-11-30|accessdate=2009-12-01|work=[[Recording_Industry_Association_of_New_Zealand|RIANZ]]|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5PkfqxTDF?url=http://www.rianz.org.nz/rianz/chart.asp|archive-date=2007-06-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和[[加拿大專輯排行榜|加拿大專輯排行榜]]<ref name="canada">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1627364/20091202/boyle_susan.jhtml|title=Susan Boyle’s Debut Smashes U.S. Chart Records|work=MTV News|accessdate=2009-12-06|archive-date=2012-07-10|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/692kypFUn?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1627364/susan-boyles-debut-smashes-us-chart-records.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>周間銷量第1位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.us/album/52113|title=Susan Boyle - I Dreamed A Dream|publisher=Music Charts|accessdate=2009-11-28|archive-date=2010-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205050120/http://acharts.us/album/52113|dead-url=no}}</ref>它亦成為了英國銷售得最快的出道專輯，打破了[[里歐娜·路易斯|里歐娜·路易斯]]2007年《Spirit》創造的記錄，根據{{link-en|尼爾森音樂統計|Nielsen SoundScan}}它在北美洲成為銷量最高的女聲獨唱出道專輯。<ref name="canada"/>樂評對這專輯的評價就毀譽參半，英國[[MSN|MSN]]的Ben Chalk給予8/10分，贊賞波伊爾的感情流露是多得她自身的人身經歷。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.uk.msn.com/reviews/articles.aspx?cp-documentid=151018761|title=I Dreamed A Dream - Susan Boyle|author=Ben Chalk|publisher=英國微軟MSN音樂網|date=2009-11-23|accessdate=2009-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126040327/http://music.uk.msn.com/reviews/articles.aspx?cp-documentid=151018761|archive-date=2009-11-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]的Bob Stanley打2/5分，批評選曲陳舊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/cd_reviews/article6923205.ece|title=Susan Boyle: I Dreamed a Dream|author=Bob Stanley|publisher=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]|date=2009-11-20|accessdate=2009-11-28}}</ref>

